##Spraying "environment-friendly enzyme" in many places not only does not prevent epidemic disease, but also promotes bacterial multiplication

Function introduction, the interface news is China has the influence original financial and economic new media, only serves the independent thinking crowd

Image: The web

REPORTER: Editor Jin Miao: Xu Yue

“

In the previous propaganda, this food waste fermentation of the "environmental enzyme" can even prevent cancer, bacteriostasis disinfection, enhance resistance.

”

“

In the previous propaganda, this food waste fermentation of the "environmental enzyme" can even prevent cancer, bacteriostasis disinfection, enhance resistance.

”

Recently, local media including Hunan Daily, Yancheng TV station and Shangrao News Network reported that local environmental authorities used so-called "environmental enzymes" to spray water trucks and disinfect roads and public toilets. During the outbreak, some enterprises and individuals involved in the "environmental enzyme" donated "environmental enzyme" to the public security, environmental protection departments, media, communities and so on. The village of East Qinyang in Jiaozuo, Henan Province, also has individuals using so-called "environment-friendly enzymes" to spray disinfection inside the village.

Information received by Liu Pengxin, a postdoctoral researcher and chemistry doctor at the Swiss Federal Institute of Technology, from netizens around the world shows that the statistics are incomplete, hefei, Zhongshan, Zhaoqing, Yancheng, Xiangyang, Xi'an, Shangrao, Hengshui and other parts of the region have been using "environmental enzymes" for disinfection.

Unlike previous plant enzymes, which are primarily proteins used in food, Liu says the so-called "eco-enzymes" are not enzymes themselves, "they are fermented swill from the skin and the sugar bacteria. "

But that's not how these enzyme companies advertise themselves.

According to a post on Wechat's public account, "Zhongshan's Environmental Enzyme Promotion Center, " the enzyme can be diluted 100,000 times, and can be used in water sprinklers, to purify streets in cities and villages, and to purify outdoor air, increase the oxygen content of the environment, decomposition of harmful pollutants in the air... help to restore the environment balance of nature, is conducive to the enhancement of human immunity; Dilution 1000-10000 times, can be used for the purification of home space. Purify Indoor Air, is conducive to the promotion of human immunity; Dilution 400 times, can be used for sterilization.

According to a report on the People's Daily Online Anhui Channel titled "Hefei Luyang District uses a fog cannon truck to spray environmental protection enzymes on 112 main and secondary trunk roads, " Li Yingxin, head of the Environmental Management Center of the city administration of Luyang District, said, the "environment-friendly Enzyme" sprayed by the "food waste skin, vegetables added Brown Sugar and water after fermentation. " And said that "diluted environment-friendly enzyme spraying, will not have any impact on the human body.

But in fact, as far as we know, so-called "eco-enzymes" may contain uncontrollable bacteria and fungi.

"This is the product of food waste fermentation, the metabolic waste of bacteria and fungi, and may contain alcohols and Aldehydes, " Liu told interface news. But because it's made by individuals from their own household food waste, each household has a different composition and produces a different metabolic waste, which is difficult to quantify precisely and may even contain potentially carcinogenic substances, such as AFLATOXINS."

"because it's fermented, it probably does contain alcohol, but there's so much in it that you can't control it, so it's definitely not sterile. "

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Named ferment beauty see news record of public number article shows, a volunteer will 100 catties"environmental protection ferment"throw into the canal inside village directly

Large-scale spraying of so-called "environmental enzymes" will not only fail to sterilize, but will spread the bacteria in the fermentation of "environmental enzymes" continuously, "Such dispersal can cause a range of problems, with bacteria and sugar sprayed into the air or attached to surfaces, like a petri dish, which may encourage other bacteria to continue to grow. "

Even the ether, 75 percent ethanol and chlorine-containing disinfectants, which are effective in inactivating the virus as described in the fifth edition of the diagnostic and treatment plan for pneumonia from COVID-19 infection, do not need to be sprayed on a large scale in non-endemic areas, Liu said, "The virus can not be separated from the Human Body long-term survival, " and some disinfectants are highly corrosive and volatile, concentration is too high to damage human health and pollution of the environment.

And Liu Pengxin's doubt lies in the city management departments or environmental protection departments around, is how to accept such without scientific verification, without quarantine, or even without the production license of products, applied to epidemic prevention.

According to Article twenty-nine of the Law of the People's Republic of China on the Prevention and control of infectious diseases, the disinfection products used for the prevention and control of infectious diseases, the drinking water supplied by drinking water supply units, and the products related to the sanitary and safe drinking water, units that produce disinfection products for the prevention and treatment of infectious diseases and those that produce disinfection products for the prevention and treatment of infectious diseases shall be subject to examination and approval by the Government of the People's Republic of China at or above the provincial level. Specific measures shall be formulated by the State Council.

In addition, according to the "disinfection management measures (2017) " , after obtaining a business license for disinfectant production enterprises, they should also obtain a health license issued by the provincial health and Family Planning Administrative Department in the locality.

The local "eco-enzyme" , all by a group called "yeast filial piety" and its "volunteers" donations, so-called "eco-enzyme" from the personal preparation, public information, the product has no relevant health certificate.

Prior to the new Crown Epidemic, the organization "fermenting filial piety" published an article saying that it can "detoxify the skin" by soaking clothes with "environment-friendly enzymes" , making self-made detergent, self-made skin care products, self-made toothpaste, etc. , the group claims daily products contain large amounts of chemicals that cause damage to the body in a process known as "transdermal toxicity" , which can lead to breast cancer, infertility and various cancers.

Liu pengxin receives the netizen information to say, Hunan local even has the organization that popularizes"Environmental Protection ferment", pass collect member fee, teach a way to absorb extensively"volunteer".

On February 9, the city administration in Luyang District, Hefei, tried spraying diluted environmental enzymes on a fog cannon truck in an attempt to clean the air on the city's roads. On February 10, the city administration of Luyang District in Hefei, Anhui Province, suspended the spraying of eco-friendly enzymes following complaints from netizens.
